/// Test group: voice groups
/// Test purpose: synth legato mode, two zones.
///
/// Test description:
/// sfz allows the creation of multiple legato zones. For instance, this allows
/// to play a legato bass, and a legato lead in the same program without one
/// legato mode interfering the other.
///
/// Play above c4, verify the legato mode. Play below c4, verify the second region.

<region> sample=..\..\samples\mono 400 looped.wav
group=1
polyphony=legato_last
hikey=b3

<region> sample=..\..\samples\mono 400 looped.wav
group=2
polyphony=legato_last
lokey=c4